These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, argentine, nigerian
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the colombian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
3. the colombian is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the argentine is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Nationality    | argentine    | nigerian | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, indian, german
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the german##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Nationality       | indian | german | canadian |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, japanese, australian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the russian is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the japanese is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Nationality         | australian     | japanese | russian |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
City: miami, boston, berlin
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person traveling to boston is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person traveling to miami is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person traveling to boston is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| City   | berlin | boston  | miami  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, bird
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the owner of the rabbit##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Pet   | ferret | bird     | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, filmmaking
House: wooden, palace, futuristic
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the palace house##1
2. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking | baking   |
| House   | futuristic     | wooden    | palace |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
City: new-york, venice, boston
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is between the owner of the turtle and the person traveling to boston##2
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| City   | boston | new-york | venice |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, poppy, dahlia
1. the person who growslily is between the person who growspoppy and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Flower    | poppy    | lily | dahlia     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, game, bolivar
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar   | bolivar   | game  | cain  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, ambient, rock
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Music-Genre       | ambient | rock | funk   |

