.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, victorian
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the victorian house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person driving the trike is the victorian house##1
4. the victorian house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| House         | farmhouse | victorian | gothic-revival |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

