The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, videographer
1. the videographer is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the australian is the videographer##1
3. the doctor is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the videographer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
