The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
