.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, swimming
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Sport   | lacrosse | swimming | tennis |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, card-games, puzzles
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | collecting  | puzzles     | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

