.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, thai, turkish
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, blood-red, chestnut
1. the american is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the person who likes white is in an odd position##4
4. the thai is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Nationality   | american | turkish | thai    |
| Color           | blood-red     | chestnut  | white |

