1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| House   | art-deco   | cape-cod          | ranch-style |

