.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea, dahlia
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Flower     | azalea  | dahlia   | bellflower |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 